啲好似連詩雅嗰啲咁既</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個同學都話要做咩科學家 考古學家 廚師咁 唔會諗搵幾多<br />\n利伸：我想做一個food chemist 👩&zwj;🔬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a3c66780f6746b2b6bbbf082db1e193081f6b4","tid":334682,"uid":13100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講到中文幾重要，升到大學無用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又黎盲反中文</blockquote><br />\n講事實就盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如你講下大學入面中文有幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你要喺香港搵工，仲要係黃口黃面，唔識中文/廣東話，邊度會搵到<br />\n你只識英文，咁點解唔直接請過白種嘅先，白種嘅擺出嚟，起碼兇到班大陸佬先<br />\n<br />\n條友仲要講嘢講到一舊舊<br />\n「讀完啲中文，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔get佢</span>言下之意。」"},{"pid":"db3d9bdd660c9e8ab26d9c8db64a45784774f31d","tid":334682,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實讀得國際學校點會想做政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：中學讀國際學校</blockquote><br />\n佢老豆做官或者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有同學老豆做警察高級個堆 都送咗對仔女去美國讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cc5b951d2eae601c99bb6fb0cb29bb4cc0d559","tid":334682,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"學中文最好聽下人講故仔先"},{"pid":"c263475141b7106ccb946c268838c258cfb1ffa1","tid":334682,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"英祖on leave <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906cdc3b25aa855e57375f2abca96d6003440605","tid":334682,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁撚有錢做政府工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港做野都係做ibank啦<br />\nbtw,政府野都係用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府做嘢係要識英文，但唔係只識英文就夠，立法會都係廣東話發言，由其毓民時代，成鳩日整啲古詩出嚟拋鳩啲官"},{"pid":"fadbec20b0c8c8127cf107ec3da2b34729873779","tid":334682,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講到中文幾重要，升到大學無用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又黎盲反中文</blockquote><br />\n講事實就盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如你講下大學入面中文有幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你要喺香港搵工，仲要係黃口黃面，唔識中文/廣東話，邊度會搵到<br />\n你只識英文，咁點解唔直接請過白種嘅先，白種嘅擺出嚟，起碼兇到班大陸佬先<br />\n<br />\n條友仲要講嘢講到一舊舊<br />\n「讀完啲中文，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔get佢</span>言下之意。」</blockquote><br />\n所以咪話睇下老夫子，識日常中文已經得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70209947038be70e44b5cb7c054f32fa4a180536","tid":334682,"uid":89316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實讀得國際學校點會想做政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm